### SpendingAnalyzer API - Testing Endpoints

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@httpUrl = http://localhost:5117

### Health Check
GET {{httpUrl}}/

### Banks

### Create Bank
POST {{httpUrl}}/api/banks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chase Bank",
  "bankAccounts": [
    {
      "name": "Checking Account",
      "balance": 5000.00
    },
    {
      "name": "Savings Account",
      "balance": 10000.00
    }
  ]
}

### Get All Banks
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/banks

### Get Bank By Id
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/banks/{bankId}

### Update Bank
PUT {{httpUrl}}/api/banks/{bankId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chase Bank - Updated"
}

### Delete Bank (Mark Inactive)
DELETE {{httpUrl}}/api/banks/{bankId}

### Bank Accounts

### Create Bank Account
POST {{httpUrl}}/api/bankaccounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bankId": "{bankId}",
  "name": "Investment Account",
  "balance": 15000.00
}

### Get All Bank Accounts
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/bankaccounts

### Get Bank Account By Id
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/bankaccounts/{accountId}

### Update Bank Account
PUT {{httpUrl}}/api/bankaccounts/{accountId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Investment Account - Updated"
}

### Set Bank Account Inactive
DELETE {{httpUrl}}/api/bankaccounts/{accountId}

### Transactions

### Create Transaction
POST {{httpUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Grocery shopping",
  "accountId": "{accountId}",
  "recipient": "Walmart",
  "amount": 150.50
}

### Get All Transactions
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/transactions

### Get Transaction By Id
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/transactions/{transactionId}

### Update Transaction
PUT {{httpUrl}}/api/transactions/{transactionId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Grocery shopping - Updated",
  "accountId": "{accountId}",
  "recipient": "Target",
  "amount": 200.00
}

### Delete Transaction
DELETE {{httpUrl}}/api/transactions/{transactionId}

### Transfers

### Create Transfer
POST {{httpUrl}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Transfer to savings",
  "sourceAccountId": "{sourceAccountId}",
  "targetAccountId": "{targetAccountId}",
  "value": 500.00
}

### Get All Transfers
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/transfers

### Get Transfer By Id
GET {{httpUrl}}/api/transfers/{transferId}

### Update Transfer
PUT {{httpUrl}}/api/transfers/{transferId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Transfer to savings - Updated",
  "sourceAccountId": "{sourceAccountId}",
  "targetAccountId": "{targetAccountId}",
  "value": 750.00
}

### Delete Transfer
DELETE {{httpUrl}}/api/transfers/{transferId}

